            <div class="title">
                Business Of The House (Production Debate)
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1941-07-15/debates/68dc8319-1c61-458d-badc-adbb45738996/WarSituation" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
