<p class="">I do not think I regard the Propaganda Debate as one which has the same far-reaching consequences upon our reputation for carrying on the war, as to reflections upon our system of production. As far as the Government are concerned, I do not think that is likely.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
